snippet.title: ALIEN XENOBLASTER - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
BUY THE GAME HERE: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2051590/ALIEN_XENOBLASTER/

== GAME DESC ==
Planet GOOBTOPIA's series of irresponsible decisions has led to a filthy wasteland polluting other planets in the solar system. Angry alien BLUNT has had enough in this arcade platformer-shooter.
